OL,5, Victims of poor service from financial 
OL,6, firms should have problems dealt with  
OL,7, speedily, particularly during uncertain
OL,8, economic times, an ombudsman has said. 
OL,10,FIt is crucial that when problems arise 
OL,11,Fthey are "addressed quickly", the chief
OL,12,Ffinancial ombudsman said.              
OL,14,FCampaigners have also been calling for 
OL,15,Fa faster response for fraud victims.   
OL,17,FEarlier this year, consumer group      
OL,18,FWhich? said people who had lost money  
OL,19,Ffaced a waiting lottery when trying to 
OL,20,Freport the situation to their bank.    
